WEBVTT

00:10:59.183 --> 00:11:01.380
But daring to know,

00:11:01.404 --> 00:11:02.974
daring to understand,

00:11:04.151 --> 00:11:07.217
means risking the possibility
that you could be wrong.

00:11:07.921 --> 00:11:10.189
It means risking the possibility

00:11:10.213 --> 00:11:14.540
that what you want and what's true
are different things.

00:11:16.070 --> 00:11:18.991
Which brings me to the third thing
that I think we need to do

00:11:19.854 --> 00:11:22.886
if we want to accept that we live
in a common reality.

00:11:22.910 --> 00:11:25.801
That third thing is:
have a little humility.

00:11:26.510 --> 00:11:28.632
By humility here, I mean
epistemic humility,

00:11:28.656 --> 00:11:30.645
which means, in a sense,